Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.61,0:07:10.24,Default,,0,0,0,,I can take off the bra straps too...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.24,0:07:12.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Whoa!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.40,0:07:12.37,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an7}Bare shoulders
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.70,0:07:14.87,Default,,0,0,0,,If it's this, then...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.12,0:07:19.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Those stupid brats will have to acknowledge...!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.25,0:07:21.50,Default,,0,0,0,,That I am...
