Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.42,0:07:24.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Hurry up!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.96,0:07:25.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Hey! You bastards!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.17,0:07:25.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Special training! Special training!
