Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.18,0:07:32.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.59,0:07:33.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Wh-whoa!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.01,0:07:39.73,Default,,0,0,0,,They're shocked and cowering now.\NAfter all, I am a B-cup!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.73,0:07:41.02,Default,,0,0,0,,This jerk is dangerous!
