Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.90,0:07:53.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Bra 101.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.74,0:07:56.87,Default,,0,0,0,,If you wear a bra without straps,\Nit can occasionally slip down,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.87,0:08:01.08,Default,,0,0,0,,and you'll end up looking like someone with\Nsuper low-hanging breasts, so be careful.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.00,0:08:06.25,Default,,0,0,0,,U-um...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.84,0:08:13.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Th-thank you... for saving me... Onee-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.85,0:08:26.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh my. They say that one can\Ncry so much the pillow gets wet,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.52,0:08:29.11,Default,,0,0,0,,but for you to cry so much\Nthat grandma's chest gets wet is, well...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.11,0:08:31.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Just what exactly happened?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.58,0:08:45.79,Default,,0,0,0,,I wonder what I have to do, in order to become\Nmore mature-looking like Lily...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.79,0:08:50.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Bras are dangerous, and my height\Nwon't increase right away, so...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.13,0:08:52.38,Default,,0,0,0,,My face?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.38,0:08:55.38,Default,,0,0,0,,If it's my face, then will it change\Neven just a little, if I put makeup on?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.38,0:08:57.55,Default,,0,0,0,,For example, even if it's just my eyebrows...!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.35,0:09:09.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, Wota, what're you laughing for...?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.52,0:09:13.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? I'm not laughing. What about you?\NThe corners of your mouth are turned up, you know.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.53,0:09:15.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, I've always had this kinda face.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.65,0:09:17.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Anyway, seriously, what're we gonna do about that?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.32,0:09:18.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, no one's saying anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.82,0:09:21.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah... That's not something that can be\Neasily brought up, you know...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.83,0:09:24.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Especially those eyebrows...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.54,0:09:27.71,Default,,0,0,0,,No can do! I can't stand it anymore!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.71,0:09:29.42,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm gonna go tease her a little!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.54,0:09:29.42,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.34,0:09:34.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Hang on a sec, Tanaka-san!\NYou're not trying to tease Loli-chan again, are you?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.09,0:09:35.13,Default,,0,0,0,,What's it to you?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.13,0:09:37.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Regardless of how she looks, she's personally\Nserious about it, so it'd be cruel, you know?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.89,0:09:40.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Then, are you saying that it's better\Nto leave her alone as she is right now?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.85,0:09:44.14,Default,,0,0,0,,You're desperately holding back\Non laughing as well, aren't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.14,0:09:45.48,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm not trying to hold back!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.31,0:09:50.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh-huh... Then what's with your hands shaking?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.31,0:09:48.69,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}She's really holding back!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.69,0:09:50.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Be careful not to cause internal bleeding.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.02,0:09:52.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Loli-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.53,0:09:53.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Lily...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.48,0:09:56.03,Default,,0,0,0,,You seem like you've got a different vibe\Nto you today than usual.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.03,0:09:57.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh...! Can you tell?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.20,0:09:59.78,Default,,0,0,0,,I decided to shape my eyebrows a bit.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.78,0:10:02.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah... They're super cute, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.33,0:10:06.50,Default,,0,0,0,,I-I think that a bit more natural look\Nwould fit you better, Loli-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.75,0:10:11.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, if it's okay with you,\Nwill you let me help you out again?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.13,0:10:12.38,Default,,0,0,0,,What?! You sure?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.38,0:10:16.67,Default,,0,0,0,,This eyebrow liner isn't coming off easily...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.13,0:10:19.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Loli-chan, you drew these by yourself, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.76,0:10:21.10,Default,,0,0,0,,What did you use?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.10,0:10:24.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Um... I shaved them with\Nthe t-shaped razor I had at home,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.31,0:10:27.60,Default,,0,0,0,,but since I shaved too much off,\NI drew them in with a 2B pencil.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.60,0:10:29.35,Default,,0,0,0,,A 2B, on top of a t-shape?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.52,0:10:34.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, there are lots of different things sold\Nlike razors for eyebrows and thin scissors,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.73,0:10:36.94,Default,,0,0,0,,so it's better if you use things like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.94,0:10:37.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.86,0:10:41.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Also, when you draw them, it's better to use stuff\Nlike eyebrow liner so that it looks more natural.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.45,0:10:44.41,Default,,0,0,0,,W-wait! Don't say it all at once! I'm gonna take notes!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.41,0:10:47.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah, well we might as well start off\Nwith shaping them, okay?
