Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.09,0:11:03.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay, it's done.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.85,0:11:06.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Wow! Amazing! Thank you, Lily!
