Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.42,0:12:19.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh...? Well... That is...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.13,0:12:22.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Just because your brains are on vacation all year\Nlong doesn't mean that you get to pick on her.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.42,0:12:22.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Huh?! Hey! What the hell?! What're doing?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.88,0:12:24.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry about this, Majime.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.88,0:12:24.59,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}My brains aren't on vacation!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.59,0:12:27.05,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Oh, not at all. Take care.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.59,0:12:26.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't just go ahead and put me on vacation!
