Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.15,0:12:38.23,Default,,0,0,0,,This is just a little something, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.23,0:12:40.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh my, that's kind of you.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.32,0:12:42.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Th-the rooms! I'll show you around!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.03,0:12:45.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's see! Over there is the living room,\Nand here's Grandma's room.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.70,0:12:46.70,Default,,0,0,0,,And then...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.82,0:12:50.66,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}That the day would come that Saku\Nwould bring her friends over...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.12,0:12:49.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Both of you, hurry up and come in. Come in.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.37,0:12:50.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you for having us over.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.66,0:12:52.33,Default,,0,0,0,,But you know, Saku...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.66,0:12:52.33,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Well then, if you will...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.33,0:12:54.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}The bathroom is here! And this is the toilet!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.87,0:12:57.21,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't think you need to show around\Nevery single room, you know....
