Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.63,0:12:59.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Wow!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.00,0:13:02.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Amazing!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.42,0:13:04.68,Default,,0,0,0,,So, this is Loli-chan's room, huh?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.68,0:13:06.18,Default,,0,0,0,,It's very feminine-like.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.18,0:13:07.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Y-you think so?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.05,0:13:11.10,Default,,0,0,0,,And you have lots of clothes!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.10,0:13:15.64,Default,,0,0,0,,P-Papa and Mama send me lots of them\Nevery month from abroad, you see.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.81,0:13:19.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Well then, shall we get started with\Ntoday's main subject right away?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.86,0:13:22.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Loli-chan's fashion study group!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.44,0:13:24.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Th-thank you in advance for your help!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.40,0:13:27.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Then, for starters, shall we have you\Ntake off everything?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.03,0:13:28.32,Default,,0,0,0,,What? Everything?
