Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.92,0:13:41.50,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm glad I came along.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.50,0:13:44.59,Default,,0,0,0,,So, which is it? Do I take it off? Or don't take it off?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.59,0:13:45.84,Default,,0,0,0,,- Take it off!\N- Don't take it off!
