Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.14,0:13:57.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, forget about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.06,0:14:00.06,Default,,0,0,0,,All right! Once more, it's the start of the study group!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.48,0:14:04.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Loli-chan, when a girl like you, who's short in height,\Nwants to wear a long skirt, then...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.36,0:14:06.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Miracle change!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.03,0:14:09.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Your top should be accented with color\Nand make the bottom a high waist!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.28,0:14:11.37,Default,,0,0,0,,By doing this, you style up!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.78,0:14:13.16,Default,,0,0,0,,You are cute!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.16,0:14:16.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Next up is, overalls, which tend to\Nend up looking rather rustic...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.29,0:14:17.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Miracle change!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.71,0:14:20.50,Default,,0,0,0,,By slipping on a long cardigan,\Nyou turn into a relaxed-cute fashionista!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.50,0:14:21.34,Default,,0,0,0,,You're right!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.34,0:14:22.63,Default,,0,0,0,,You are relaxed-cute!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.75,0:14:25.84,Default,,0,0,0,,You coordinate a boyish-look with girly hair\Nto create a gap in styles.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.17,0:14:27.30,Default,,0,0,0,,S-so cute...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.30,0:14:29.93,Default,,0,0,0,,In addition, something like this, where you\Nloosely wear a course-knit one-piece.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.93,0:14:32.14,Default,,0,0,0,,See, even just this is cute, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.14,0:14:33.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Honestly! You're too cute!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.06,0:14:36.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh! I see!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.18,0:14:40.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Crap... We haven't said\Nanything but cute for a while now.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.90,0:14:42.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Well...
