Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.12,0:14:55.37,Default,,0,0,0,,You big-boobed buster!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.37,0:14:56.20,Default,,0,0,0,,B-buster?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.20,0:15:01.17,Default,,0,0,0,,At times, obsequiousness and modesty can\Nirritate people, you know. So, keep that in mind!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.17,0:15:02.58,Default,,0,0,0,,M-my apologies.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.58,0:15:03.67,Default,,0,0,0,,That was lucky!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.92,0:15:08.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Majime, do you want to study\Nhow to become cuter too?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.05,0:15:11.59,Default,,0,0,0,,What? Well, of course, if I could be,\Nthen I'd want to, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.59,0:15:12.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Then let's do that!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.10,0:15:14.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's go to Majime's house right now,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.56,0:15:16.97,Default,,0,0,0,,and then Majime, you can have\Na fashion study group too!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.97,0:15:18.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Sounds good! Let's go! Let's go!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.81,0:15:20.52,Default,,0,0,0,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.10,0:15:23.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Aw! I'm hungry! Let's eat something!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.86,0:15:24.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.44,0:15:27.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?! Salted green onion kalbi bowl?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.73,0:15:30.36,Default,,0,0,0,,You're kidding me!\NObviously, something like that's gonna be tasty!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.37,0:15:37.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Hmm?! Damn it! How dare they season it with\Nsesame oil! Well of course it's tasty!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.74,0:15:41.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, what're you having over there?\NHuh?! A soft-boiled egg pork cutlet bowl?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.25,0:15:44.50,Default,,0,0,0,,There it is! How dare they think they can\Njust make it a soft-boiled egg...! Fine!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.50,0:15:46.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Soft-boiled gooeyness is like righteous!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.00,0:15:46.17,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Shut up!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.17,0:15:49.09,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}When Wota consumes something delicious,\N{\an8}she loses it, you know...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.17,0:15:49.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Of course, it's delicious! Not to mention, it's pork loin!\NIt's gonna be invincible dripping with fat!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.09,0:15:52.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Robo, what's yours?! A juicy deep-fried bowl?!\NAre you kidding me?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.43,0:15:54.34,Default,,0,0,0,,It even has tartar sauce over it?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.34,0:15:57.39,Default,,0,0,0,,That's totally breaking the rules! It's like the best!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.06,0:16:01.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Big Sis!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.52,0:16:04.81,Default,,0,0,0,,My friends are here to hang out right now, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.81,0:16:07.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Actually, they all really want to meet you, Big Sis.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.94,0:16:10.28,Default,,0,0,0,,So, she's Kohaku-chan's older twin sister.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.28,0:16:12.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Then that means she's the same age as us, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.45,0:16:14.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Do they look alike then?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.45,0:16:15.45,Default,,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.45,0:16:17.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Then go ahead and make it sound like I've died.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.83,0:16:18.74,Default,,0,0,0,,I will not!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.74,0:16:22.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Today's visitations have ended\N{\an8}(except Kohaku).
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.54,0:16:22.50,Default,,0,0,0,,I-I'm sorry. Big Sis is considerably shy, so...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.50,0:16:25.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Big Sister, wanna chat with us?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.08,0:16:26.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's hang out together!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.42,0:16:28.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Big Sis, it's not scary!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.88,0:16:32.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh! A translucent Michael Jackson!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.63,0:16:34.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Here goes!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.80,0:16:35.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Wow! So cute!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.89,0:16:36.76,Default,,0,0,0,,So alike!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.76,0:16:38.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh no! You tricked me, Kohaku!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.39,0:16:39.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.18,0:16:41.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh yeah! Big Sis is very good at fortune telling!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.81,0:16:42.60,Default,,0,0,0,,What?! Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.60,0:16:43.44,Default,,0,0,0,,That's amazing!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.44,0:16:44.35,Default,,0,0,0,,What kinda fortune telling?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.98,0:16:47.23,Default,,0,0,0,,And, there you go...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.23,0:16:49.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Wow! Amazing! She nailed it!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.02,0:16:51.49,Default,,0,0,0,,What?! Then I want you to read my fortune next!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.49,0:16:53.53,Default,,0,0,0,,I wonder if I can get a boyfriend by Christmas.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.74,0:16:53.07,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}O-okay...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.53,0:16:54.61,Default,,0,0,0,,What?! Me first...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.83,0:17:02.66,Default,,0,0,0,,The time is coming soon,\Nwhen the one inside me is going to awaken...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.41,0:17:05.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Stop! Please stop!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.67,0:17:09.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Please don't...! Rage inside of meeeeeee!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.59,0:17:10.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.59,0:17:13.30,Default,,0,0,0,,If you're not gonna eat your meal right away,\NI'm gonna clean it up!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.64,0:17:20.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Wow! Welcome!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.06,0:17:23.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Kanade's friends? Come in. Come in.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.14,0:17:26.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Th-thank you for having us over...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.02,0:17:27.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Th-thank you...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.40,0:17:30.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Jeez. If you'd told me sooner,\Nthen I would've baked a cake or something.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.57,0:17:33.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, my apologies. Shall I go buy one\Nat the cake shop in front of the train station?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.48,0:17:35.07,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Th-this is...!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.65,0:17:36.61,Default,,0,0,0,,But that place's fresh whipped cream\Nis a little off, you know.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.28,0:17:42.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Yum! They're like an extravagant salmon-ikura bowl!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.45,0:17:42.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an7}Salmon\NIkura
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.37,0:17:43.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Wow!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.95,0:17:47.00,Default,,0,0,0,,So elastic!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.00,0:17:48.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Mom?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.08,0:17:50.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, she's so cute!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.34,0:17:52.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, of course she's cute, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.25,0:17:54.26,Default,,0,0,0,,This girl over here is super pretty too!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.59,0:17:55.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Jeez! Mom!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.92,0:17:59.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Aw! It's fine! I'm having them share\Ntheir youthful essence with me, so...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.43,0:17:59.43,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Oh...!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.76,0:18:01.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Someya-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.89,0:18:08.69,Default,,0,0,0,,N-now then, once again, the fashion study group starts!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.69,0:18:11.73,Default,,0,0,0,,First off, let us take a look at Kanade's closet!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.73,0:18:12.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Aye!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.11,0:18:14.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an7}Sweats
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.28,0:18:14.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an7}Sweats\N{\an7}Shirts
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.44,0:18:14.61,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an7}Sweats\N{\an8}Shirts\N{\an7}Shirts
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.61,0:18:14.82,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an7}Sweats\N{\an8}Shirts\N{\an8}Shirts\N{\an7}Shirts
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.82,0:18:15.19,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an7}Sweats\N{\an8}Shirts\N{\an8}Shirts\N{\an7}Shirts\N{\an8}Shirts
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.19,0:18:15.82,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an7}Sweats\N{\an8}Shirts\N{\an9}Sweats\N{\an8}Shirts\N{\an7}Shirts\N{\an8}Shirts
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.94,0:18:17.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you a middle school boy?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.61,0:18:20.49,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm not good at thinking up coordinated outfits, so...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.49,0:18:22.95,Default,,0,0,0,,In general, I make do with about two or three styles.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.95,0:18:24.33,Default,,0,0,0,,You are a middle school boy...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.33,0:18:26.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Lily, I'm begging you! Please save Majime!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.50,0:18:29.96,Default,,0,0,0,,When you plead that desperately,\Nthat does hurt my feelings, you know...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.42,0:18:35.01,Default,,0,0,0,,We've got no choice. We'll go shopping\Nfor clothes again some other time and...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.01,0:18:37.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's make today a study group about hair styles!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.42,0:18:38.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Y-yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.38,0:18:39.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Aye!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.13,0:18:40.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Here goes!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.39,0:18:42.85,Default,,0,0,0,,For short hair that tends to end up too boyish...!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.85,0:18:44.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Miracle change!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.14,0:18:46.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Braided arrangement!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.68,0:18:48.73,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't do something like this on my own...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.73,0:18:50.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Silky straight with an iron!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.60,0:18:52.31,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't do this on my own.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.31,0:18:54.98,Default,,0,0,0,,A pompadour-style arrangement with a hair pin!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.98,0:18:57.11,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't feel like I could do this on my own...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.11,0:18:58.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Wow! Majime, you're cute!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.32,0:19:02.91,Default,,0,0,0,,H-huh... But it's not something\Nthat I could do on my own at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.91,0:19:07.16,Default,,0,0,0,,What?! Hey! What's with that "I can't do this\Non my own" thing you keep saying?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.29,0:19:11.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, if someone else does it for me,\Nthen I could possibly change temporarily,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.96,0:19:14.42,Default,,0,0,0,,but I guess I'm saying that there's no point\Nif I can't do it on my own.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.63,0:19:18.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey you! Do you think the girls of the world\Njust naturally become cute or something?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.59,0:19:21.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Everyone makes an effort, you know! Effort!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.05,0:19:23.43,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Hey! Wait! Please... Don't knead them...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.93,0:19:23.43,Default,,0,0,0,,It's the same as that studying you're so good at!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.43,0:19:27.27,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Oh...! Ah...! Not... Not there...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.43,0:19:27.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Were you dangling both of these tremendous things\Nwithout knowing something like that?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.89,0:19:28.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Well?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.73,0:19:29.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Majime!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.77,0:19:30.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.85,0:19:32.77,Default,,0,0,0,,It is just as you say, Someya-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.77,0:19:37.78,Default,,0,0,0,,I thought that without a doubt, the women of\Nthe world naturally acquired fashion senses.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.78,0:19:40.03,Default,,0,0,0,,I will try to make a little more effort to do so...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.03,0:19:41.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Majime! Let's do our best together!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.86,0:19:42.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.07,0:19:44.66,Default,,0,0,0,,It's fine if you understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.45,0:19:49.16,Default,,0,0,0,,A child who so disliked fashion is...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.45,0:19:49.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Let's master fashion together!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.16,0:19:51.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes. Until we're called fashion leaders!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.54,0:19:51.67,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}The influence from friends is amazing...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.67,0:19:54.25,Default,,0,0,0,,If I make an effort, I'll be able to become\Nbig like you, Majime, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.08,0:19:54.75,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}(T-h-a-n-k y-o-u.)
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.25,0:19:55.17,Default,,0,0,0,,If you make an effort, then for sure!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.67,0:20:03.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you very much for today.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.14,0:20:05.85,Default,,0,0,0,,M-me too. I really learned a lot!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.51,0:20:07.89,Default,,0,0,0,,You're welcome.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.89,0:20:10.85,Default,,0,0,0,,It feels like all we've done is\Njust receive your help, Someya-san...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.85,0:20:12.35,Default,,0,0,0,,We should reciprocate in some way.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.35,0:20:15.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Plus, I haven't shown my gratitude\Nfor the bras and eyebrow stuff.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.06,0:20:17.48,Default,,0,0,0,,What? I already received a lot!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.48,0:20:18.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.57,0:20:19.99,Default,,0,0,0,,You see, that would be...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.99,0:20:21.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Lots of...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.32,0:20:27.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Side... dish... es!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.08,0:20:29.83,Default,,0,0,0,,But since I can't say that...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.29,0:20:32.75,Default,,0,0,0,,The fun memories I have of both of you!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.17,0:20:35.96,Default,,0,0,0,,S..Someya-san?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.29,0:20:39.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Lily! You're a super good person!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.75,0:20:41.51,Default,,0,0,0,,I hope you'll continue to be there for me, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.51,0:20:42.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.13,0:20:43.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Likewise!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.05,0:20:45.76,Default,,0,0,0,,All right! I'm gonna work harder to be fashionable!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.43,0:20:52.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey Wota, what's up with her this time...?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.85,0:20:56.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Stop that. I'm at my limit in a lot of ways right now...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.35,0:20:57.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Even the actual person in question...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.36,0:21:00.90,Default,,0,0,0,,apparently knows she might have\Ngone too far this time...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.69,0:21:03.86,Default,,0,0,0,,In terms of those bangs...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.99,0:21:07.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Instead of becoming fashionable...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.99,0:21:07.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Last night, I was up until midnight studying the\Nfashion site that you told me about, Someya-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.91,0:21:09.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh! Loli-chan's here.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.83,0:21:11.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Loli-chan, morning!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.58,0:21:12.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Good morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.58,0:21:13.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh... Good mo-
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.88,0:21:23.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey! You guys! Don't you be hurting\NLoli-chan's feelings like that again!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.09,0:21:27.14,Default,,0,0,0,,It's best if you think about\Ndeoxyribonucleic acid, you know.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.43,0:21:30.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Just what exactly happened?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.14,0:21:34.10,Default,,0,0,0,,You look cute like a kokeshi doll.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.10,0:21:39.27,Default,,0,0,0,,No! Grandma, please give me your bangs!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.27,0:21:42.57,Default,,0,0,0,,There you go talking nonsense again. This child...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.46,0:22:06.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Noisy and loud
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.13,0:22:10.68,Default,,0,0,0,,But also endearing
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.05,0:22:14.89,Default,,0,0,0,,The laughter from that day
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.89,0:22:18.90,Default,,0,0,0,,A story that can't be rewound
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.90,0:22:22.77,Default,,0,0,0,,The thing about youth is, it's always light and shadows
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.77,0:22:24.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Inside the darkness
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.82,0:22:26.86,Default,,0,0,0,,A shining inferior star
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.07,0:22:30.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Looking back are complicated
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.57,0:22:35.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Far too beautiful days
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.58,0:22:44.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Springtime has always passed by unexpectedly by then
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.59,0:22:51.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Your words reverberate in my heart
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.64,0:23:00.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Someday springtime will take it all away
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.15,0:23:07.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Until that day, being stupid is all right
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.15,0:23:12.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Because I'll run past it
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.62,0:23:18.00,Default,,0,0,0,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:18.20,0:23:19.71,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}LIKE\NNot fair!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:19.71,0:23:24.46,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an7}Stop being\N{\an7}so clingy!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:19.91,0:23:22.79,Default,,0,0,0,,What?! Long blond hair and sanpaku eyes.\NYounger in age delinquent bottom!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.79,0:23:24.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Black-haired glasses-wearing average Joe.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:24.38,0:23:26.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Crybaby working adult member of society\Nand bullied child, who's a top?!
